  "detailed_description": "<h1>Other shmup games</h1><p><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>A shoot’em up game with bite-size levels about diving into the hole inside a giant meteor and stops it from crashing to the earth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354460/extras/16fb33b8dd06904c401dccd094caab8c.apng?t=1721697278\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354460/extras/16fb33b8dd06904c401dccd094caab8c.poster.avif?t=1721697278\" class=\"bb_img\" width=384 height=384 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Battle through many different areas with unique enemies<br></li><li> Boss fight.<br></li><li> Weird and unique graphics with retro vibes.<br></li><li> Play solo or couch co-op with your friend.<br></li><li> Power by PICO-8.<br></li><li> Support joysticks.<br></li><li> Music from Pico-8 Tune by @gruber_music​<br></li><li> Come with the raspberry pi build.<br></li><li> Latest version. (May 2021) move draw layer of enemy bullets to the top.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "A shoot’em up game with bite-size levels about diving into the hole inside a giant meteor and stops it from crashing to the earth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354460/extras/16fb33b8dd06904c401dccd094caab8c.apng?t=1721697278\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1354460/extras/16fb33b8dd06904c401dccd094caab8c.poster.avif?t=1721697278\" class=\"bb_img\" width=384 height=384 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Battle through many different areas with unique enemies<br></li><li> Boss fight.<br></li><li> Weird and unique graphics with retro vibes.<br></li><li> Play solo or couch co-op with your friend.<br></li><li> Power by PICO-8.<br></li><li> Support joysticks.<br></li><li> Music from Pico-8 Tune by @gruber_music​<br></li><li> Come with the raspberry pi build.<br></li><li> Latest version. (May 2021) move draw layer of enemy bullets to the top.</li></ul>",
